1035
01:00:42.752 --> 01:00:45.742
And we found that indeed, we see global dysregulation of brain.

1036
01:00:45.802 --> 01:00:49.572
But just to give you a small vignette, one area of particular increase of

1037
01:00:49.642 --> 01:00:53.562
activity was actually the VTA, which is a second order or

1038
01:00:53.602 --> 01:00:57.102
a much higher order connection. It's not a direct synapse from the lung to the

1039
01:00:57.182 --> 01:01:00.502
brain. So it was really particular that we saw a very clear increase in this

1040
01:01:00.542 --> 01:01:04.294
particular region itself.So we use calcium

1041
01:01:04.354 --> 01:01:08.334
