1054
01:01:53.814 --> 01:01:57.254
then dampens with the vagotomy, really

1055
01:01:57.294 --> 01:02:01.214
suggesting that these are signals that are functioning through the

1056
01:02:01.234 --> 01:02:01.734
vagus.

1057
01:02:02.834 --> 01:02:05.974
Importantly, we wanted to understand whether that

1058
01:02:06.414 --> 01:02:10.324
translates to any functional deficits in these mice that have this

1059
01:02:10.374 --> 01:02:11.794
altered circuitry within the brain.

1060
01:02:12.214 --> 01:02:14.934
And indeed, as the VTA is known for a lot of

1061
01:02:15.254 --> 01:02:18.864
motivation and discrimination, we performed a battery of

1062
01:02:19.034 --> 01:02:22.824
tests. I'm just showing you an example here, where we actually do see a

1063
01:02:22.894 --> 01:02:26.674
change in the phenotype of these animals in terms of how they behave

1064
01:02:27.294 --> 01:02:29.974
in the context of motivation.

1065
01:02:30.894 --> 01:02:34.804
And so I think it's a really exciting time to, again, just start thinking about how

1066
01:02:34.834 --> 01:02:38.704
